80
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:51,240
-What do you need to prepare?
-Present. Birthday present.

81
00:05:51,599 --> 00:05:53,840
-Whose present?
-Who else?

82
00:05:55,919 --> 00:05:57,240
Li Ming Cheng again?

83
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,919
It's the most important day of the year.

84
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,680
It's has been a tradition
for many years.

85
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:05,960
-How can I forget it this year?
-What tradition?

86
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,919
Brother Ming Cheng.

87
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,800
Brother Ming Cheng.

88
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:14,560
Your birthday is almost here.

89
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,000
What present do you want?

90
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:19,680
Full marks for Mathematics and English.
As for Language,

91
00:06:20,479 --> 00:06:21,319
95 marks.

92
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:24,440
This is what you always got.
It's so simple.

93
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,240
I'm talking about you.

94
00:06:29,479 --> 00:06:32,440
Brother, can you set
an easier wish for me?

95
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,159
Full marks for Mathematics then.

96
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,879
If you can realise that,

97
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,599
I'll fulfil any of your requests...

98
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,079
on your next month's birthday.

99
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,120
Really?

100
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,280
I promise.

101
00:06:44,079 --> 00:06:45,599
But you failed, right?

102
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,240
That was the one time I had
full marks for a subject.

103
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,479
The test paper even fell into the water.

104
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:54,319
From then on, we made a promise...

105
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,520
to send each other birthday present
every year.

106
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,560
If I manage to guess what he likes,

107
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:01,599
he will send me something
I like during my birthday.

108
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:03,919
I was thinking that...

109
00:07:04,159 --> 00:07:06,359
maybe he might realise it one day...

110
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:09,759
and give himself to me
as present during my birthday.

111
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:12,840
You think too much.

112
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:14,359
But the thing is,

113
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,359
I need to guess what he likes.

114
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:21,159
But I hadn't guessed it right
for many years already.

115
00:07:21,479 --> 00:07:23,240
Is it that hard to guess?

116
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:26,039
The problem is,
his presents are too strange.

117
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,840
Do you know what he gave me last year?

118
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:30,039
CET-4 vocabulary.

119
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:32,039
And he asked me to pass
the exam this year.

120
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,960
If I don't get it right again,

121
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:37,120
he might give me some
tuition audio cards...

122
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:38,960
and force me to listen to all of them.

123
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,599
It's so scary when I think of that.

124
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,159
Can't you just ask him?

125
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,400
I can't.

126
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,400
It'll be pointless then.

127
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,800
That's not true.
You can ask his friends.

128
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:51,759
I'm just a mediocre student.

129
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:54,159
Do you think I'll know any study-tyrant?

130
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,079
And I can't get into their club.

131
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:59,400
Moreover, they are trying to flatter
senior Zhang Ran Yu lately.

132
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,759
They treat me like air
every time I go there.

133
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,919
Looks like I have to help you myself.

134
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:07,560
Tell me, which guy
do you want to target?

135
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:12,039
Have you passed your CET-6?

136
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,240
Have you gotten a prize
from competition?

137
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:16,759
Looks is not the
only thing they look at.

138
00:08:16,919 --> 00:08:19,479
Do I have to get my IQ
tested to join a club?

139
