151
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:03,399
The simpler the relationship,
the deeper he'll sink into it.

152
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:06,279
Look at him.
He even got dark circles now.

153
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:07,919
Can you imagine?

154
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,080
He lived like a veteran before this.

155
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,560
He'll sleep at nine every day
no matter what.

156
00:09:12,719 --> 00:09:15,000
Do you know who that friend is?

157
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:16,839
I'm not really sure.

158
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:19,519
But he mentioned it before.

159
00:09:19,839 --> 00:09:21,080
I think it's a girl.

160
00:09:22,551 --> 00:09:24,471
[Confirm your surrender?]
[Yes.]

161
00:09:27,663 --> 00:09:29,513
[Do you want to play another round?]

162
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:33,560
[No. I'm busy today.]

163
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:43,262
[No wonder you seem hasty today.]

164
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:48,865
[Is it something very important?]

165
00:09:52,641 --> 00:09:54,641
[Yes. I'm on my way
to destroy a dumb club.]

166
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:05,440
-Isn't that her? She is here.
-It's you.

167
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:06,760
I'm here to register.

168
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:09,760
I received a notice about admission.
It's still effective, right?

169
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,039
Yes, it is.

170
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:16,359
I never thought that
you'll be coming to our club.

171
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,560
Can I go in now?

172
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,240
Of course.

173
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,640
We have a new member? Welcome.

174
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:26,000
-Let me introduce you to her. She...
-No need.

175
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:28,000
She is the face of Kwang Hua University.

176
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,359
Who doesn't know her?

177
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,320
You...

178
00:10:32,839 --> 00:10:35,240
You are the one who called me barred...

179
00:10:35,399 --> 00:10:36,760
Barred spiral galaxy.

180
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:39,039
-Senior.
-Don't be mad.

181
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:40,919
-Don't be mad.
-Don't think too much, Ran Yu.

182
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,440
It's just a code name.

183
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,080
How could you recruit her?

184
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,719
She got full marks for
the club admission test.

185
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:47,959
So what?

186
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:50,039
You can't be sure that she didn't cheat.

187
00:10:51,719 --> 00:10:55,479
Calcium oxide, antimony,
copper sulfate pentahydrate.

188
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:56,640
What?

189
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,440
-What is she saying?
-It's nothing.

190
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,800
-That's right.
-You heard her wrong.

191
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:01,959
Bi Qiu Jing,

192
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:06,399
I have a newcomer information file
for you. Please come with me.

193
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:15,039
-It has now started.
-Let's see.

194
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:17,200
Our president is going to
teach her a lesson now.

195
00:11:17,959 --> 00:11:20,240
Really? That's the least he could do.

196
00:11:21,359 --> 00:11:23,719
Let me state this first. I'm not mad.

197
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,000
I'm just worried that he'll be tricked.

198
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,159
-That's right.
-We understand.

199
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,880
-Senior, let's continue.
-Come.

200
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:30,680
Have a seat.

201
