Your club is really shabby.

202
00:11:39,159 --> 00:11:41,039
You don't even have a private office.

203
00:11:42,919 --> 00:11:44,200
If I remember correctly,

204
00:11:44,359 --> 00:11:47,839
you are a third-year student from
Kwang Hua's Chemistry Faculty, right?

205
00:11:49,039 --> 00:11:50,159
Zhou Shi told you that?

206
00:11:50,599 --> 00:11:53,039
Don't underestimate your popularity
in this campus.

207
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:56,479
The professor in the Chemistry Faculty
complains that if you are in the class,

208
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,719
it'll basically become
a mistake-correcting class.

209
00:11:58,919 --> 00:12:01,440
In the end, you even taught
the class in his stead.

210
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:04,200
You are really one of a kind.

211
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:07,039
Is that so? Which professor it is?

212
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,880
The molecular formula of calcium oxide,

213
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:10,159
element code of antimony...

214
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,640
and the molecular weight of
copper sulfate pentahydrate.

215
00:12:12,839 --> 00:12:14,800
You haven't forgotten
about these, right?

216
00:12:21,839 --> 00:12:25,279
So, this is the translation of
what you said just now.

217
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:27,519
Bi Qiu Jing.

218
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:30,159
You shouldn't use
your knowledge like this.

219
00:12:30,479 --> 00:12:32,800
After all, we are all in the same club.

220
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,399
Isn't it good to get along
with each other?

221
00:12:35,599 --> 00:12:37,880
I didn't come here
to be friends with them.

222
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:40,680
I came here for you.

223
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:45,399
Me?

224
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,760
Do you have a girl you like now?

225
00:12:58,959 --> 00:13:00,399
No changes in your pupils.

226
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:04,800
Your heart is not beating fast.

227
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:06,719
Looks like the answer is no.

228
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:09,719
Okay. Your birthday is on the 6th.

229
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:11,240
What present do you want?

230
00:13:14,359 --> 00:13:15,440
Bi Qiu Jing.

231
00:13:15,919 --> 00:13:19,399
With our relationship right now,

232
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:23,120
don't you think this is
too early for that?

233
00:13:23,719 --> 00:13:24,640
Relationship?

234
00:13:25,399 --> 00:13:26,839
What kind of relationship you want?

235
00:13:27,599 --> 00:13:29,560
At least a relationship where...

236
00:13:29,839 --> 00:13:31,279
we can celebrate birthday together.

237
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:33,959
If you treat me to a meal, I'll go.

238
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:36,120
So, can you answer my question now?

239
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,560
A full set of deep space
photography equipment.

240
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:43,080
You want to capture the nebula map
in the suburbs, right?

241
00:13:43,359 --> 00:13:44,880
It's going to be new moon soon.

242
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:46,719
It's a good timing for that.

243
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:48,959
Did you study about this too?

244
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:53,159
You need an equatorial mount
and a laptop too.

245
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:56,000
Yes. I need optical axis calibration
equipment and guide mirror too.

246
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:58,159
Rejected. These are too expensive.

247
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,320
Can't you think about something simpler?

248
00:14:01,159 --> 00:14:05,080
A reduced version of the
solar system star model.

249
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,519
It's still expensive.

250
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:10,320
And you can't find it here.
You have to purchase it overseas.

251
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:11,800
Change to another one.

252
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:14,919
Collection of NASA astrophotography.

253
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:18,279
I have to look for the source and
download it. So time-consuming.

254
00:14:18,959 --> 00:14:22,080
Can't you think about something that
a normal person can get their hands on?

255
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:25,599
It'll be best if it's something DIY
that doesn't need money.

256
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:33,479
Is this Chinese
calligraphy writing yours?

257
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,800
Not bad.

258
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:40,000
-Yes. Sometimes, I'll write it.
-Good.

259
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,440
A Chinese calligraphy writing then.

260
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:44,000
Chinese calligraphy writing?

261
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,240
From now on,

262
00:14:46,560 --> 00:14:49,640
it'll be your ideal birthday present.

263
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,800
If Zhou Shi asks you about it,
tell her that.

264
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,399
Understand? Say it exactly like that.

265
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,919
-Why?
-For no particular reason.

266
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:59,800
As for the expensive and troublesome
things that you want,

267
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:03,080
-I'll find a way to get them for you.
-Really?

268
00:15:03,399 --> 00:15:04,359
I'll do my best.

269
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:07,479
But I'll be the one to decide
when and how to get them.

270
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:08,880
You can't have any objections.

271
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:10,359
Alright.

272
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:22,279
Come in.

273
00:15:29,519 --> 00:15:31,680
Not bad. You look good.

274
00:15:31,919 --> 00:15:33,599
It suits the environment of our gallery.

275
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,279
Thank you for giving me this chance.

276
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:38,359
Although I'm not really sure
what should I do exactly ,

277
00:15:38,519 --> 00:15:41,080
from now on, I'll work hard.

278
00:15:41,959 --> 00:15:43,159
No need for that.

279
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:46,560
As you can see.
Our business here is not doing well.

280
00:15:46,959 --> 00:15:49,279
We only have customers once in a while.

281
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,880
And they are frequent visitors.

282
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:53,560
They know about paintings very well.

283
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:55,760
Even without your guidance
and recommendation,

284
00:15:55,919 --> 00:15:57,200
they'll still buy it.

285
00:15:58,120 --> 00:16:01,240
But I can't just do nothing.

286
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:02,519
You...

287
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:06,159
just need to stand
at the entrance and smile.

288
00:16:07,719 --> 00:16:10,440
Another thing.
Don't wear heels tomorrow.

289
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:11,880
You have to stand the whole day.

290
00:16:12,359 --> 00:16:13,599
Your legs will break.

291
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:15,440
-Thank you.
-Come in.

292
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:21,240
Director He.

293
00:16:22,359 --> 00:16:23,560
He is here.

294
00:16:24,599 --> 00:16:25,640
Said that I'm not here.

295
00:16:25,839 --> 00:16:27,279
I already told him. But Chair...

296
00:16:29,359 --> 00:16:30,959
But he doesn't believe me.

297
00:16:32,519 --> 00:16:33,919
So annoying.

298
00:16:36,159 --> 00:16:36,919
Xiao Zhou.

299
00:16:37,479 --> 00:16:38,880
Help me tell him this.

300
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,640
If he insisted on waiting,

301
00:16:40,959 --> 00:16:42,039
tell him that...

302
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:44,440
I'm feeling ill and not fit enough
to meet a client.

303
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,120
Alright.

304
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,640
That person...

305
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,880
sounds so cold.

306
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:04,680
Is he the one Director He hates?

307
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:09,519
-You?
-You?

308
00:17:11,119 --> 00:17:12,919
Did you put a tapping device on my body?

309
00:17:13,039 --> 00:17:14,720
You are here again on
my first day of work.

310
00:17:14,879 --> 00:17:16,680
Why can't I get rid of you?

311
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:19,600
-Let go of me.
-This is really by chance.

312
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:21,639
I'm here to meet Director He.

313
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:26,759
So, that man is you?

314
00:17:26,919 --> 00:17:28,600
-What?
-Nothing.

315
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:31,039
She feels ill today.

316
00:17:31,999 --> 00:17:33,039
So, she can't meet you.

317
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:36,960
Her body is ill again.

318
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:38,720
Tell her this.

319
00:17:39,119 --> 00:17:42,720
The chairman is here for official
business. Ask her to bear with it.

320
00:17:43,399 --> 00:17:44,720
Chairman?

321
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:47,200
What? She didn't tell you this?

322
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:50,159
This gallery is under Yun Ma Artwork.

323
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:51,759
So, in the end,

324
00:17:51,999 --> 00:17:53,360
I'm still working under you?

325
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,039
Why is it?

326
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,800
You want to quit?

327
00:17:57,159 --> 00:17:58,840
Why would I quit?

328
00:17:59,399 --> 00:18:01,239
I'm hired by Director He.

329
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:04,200
Even if you are the chairman,
you can't just fire me.

330
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:07,600
Don't worry. I'm here this time...

331
00:18:07,759 --> 00:18:09,720
to have a talk with Director He.

332
00:18:09,999 --> 00:18:11,239
I don't care about other things.

333
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:13,680
No matter what, I have to see her today.

334
00:18:13,919 --> 00:18:15,879
-Go now.
-Alright then.

335
00:18:16,119 --> 00:18:17,680
Please wait. I'll tell her that now.

336
00:18:19,879 --> 00:18:20,639
Quickly.

337
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:28,720
You and she are quite fated
to meet each other.

338
00:18:28,919 --> 00:18:31,960
Yes. Every time she
tries to hide from me,

339
00:18:32,159 --> 00:18:35,119
she'll always end up being by my side.

340
00:18:46,759 --> 00:18:49,320
Director He asked you
to go to her office.

341
00:18:49,560 --> 00:18:51,440
She said not to affect
the gallery's business.

342
00:18:51,639 --> 00:18:53,200
Affect the gallery's business?

343
00:18:57,399 --> 00:18:59,519
I don't think it needs my help.

344
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,279
Lead the way.

345
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,119
Oh my goodness. This is so suffocating.

346
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:54,879
Why are they so serious with each other?

347
00:19:55,119 --> 00:19:57,720
Their relationship
has always been like that.

348
00:19:58,279 --> 00:19:59,600
Seriously?

349
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,680
But from what I heard from Xiao Fei,

350
00:20:01,919 --> 00:20:03,440
they are mother and son.

351
00:20:06,119 --> 00:20:07,840
Is she his stepmother?

352
00:20:08,919 --> 00:20:09,999
Biological mother.

353
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:13,360
Why are they so estranged then?

354
00:20:13,519 --> 00:20:15,800
They call each other
chairman and Director He.

355
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:18,239
Those who don't know will
think that they are rivals.

356
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:20,720
Director He hasn't used his name...

357
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,320
for a very long time already.

358
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:26,239
Is it because...

359
00:20:26,840 --> 00:20:28,399
Wei Qing is not filial?

360
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:31,279
If only it's that simple.

361
00:20:32,879 --> 00:20:35,320
Their relationship is hard to explain
in a few words.

362
00:20:36,119 --> 00:20:37,480
If there's a chance,

363
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:39,759
it's better if he tells you himself.

364
00:20:40,159 --> 00:20:42,360
Forget it. It's so awkward
to even think of it.

365
00:20:44,999 --> 00:20:48,360
Chairman, why are you here?

366
00:20:53,039 --> 00:20:55,159
The girl who brought in
the coffees just now...

367
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:57,039
is hired by you, Director He?

368
00:20:57,759 --> 00:20:58,519
Yes.

369
00:20:59,560 --> 00:21:01,879
She is just an art student who
has yet to graduate, right?

370
00:21:02,159 --> 00:21:05,879
With her experiences, she can't handle
the clients in the gallery, right?

371
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:08,600
She can learn if she is inexperienced.

372
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:12,360
Chairman, you are already quite busy.

373
00:21:12,560 --> 00:21:14,600
No need to care about measly things...

374
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:16,399
like personnel recruitment.

375
00:21:17,039 --> 00:21:18,919
Personnel recruitment is a measly thing.

376
00:21:19,360 --> 00:21:20,560
What about deficit then?

377
00:21:33,239 --> 00:21:35,119
The shareholder meeting
will be held next month.

378
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:36,720
With this kind of situation,

379
00:21:36,999 --> 00:21:39,560
Are you planning to be held accountable
at the shareholder meeting?

380
00:21:39,919 --> 00:21:43,560
If this deficit continues, during the
shareholder meeting next year,

381
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:45,840
they'll decrease the budget
for the gallery.

382
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:47,960
And they'll lay off
a large number of workers.

383
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:51,080
If it really comes to that,

384
00:21:51,759 --> 00:21:54,999
sooner or later, you'll be stripped
from your position.

385
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:56,960
Chairman.

386
00:21:58,239 --> 00:22:01,879
Are you here today
to warn me specifically...

387
00:22:02,080 --> 00:22:04,480
or are you here to fire me?

388
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,919
I will never allow that from happening.

389
00:22:07,999 --> 00:22:10,960
Is that so? Then what is your plan?

390
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:16,560
Recruit more famous painters
to increase the gallery's turnover.

391
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:17,639
I disagree.

392
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:19,879
Ever since Yun Ma Artwork
was established,

393
00:22:20,039 --> 00:22:21,999
we've never put profit first.

394
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:25,399
Instead, we focus on
cultivating new artists.

395
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:28,720
If you just care about
recruiting famous painters,

396
00:22:28,879 --> 00:22:32,159
then what advantages
we'll have against other galleries?

397
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:35,680
All these years, I knew that you've
been putting a lot of effort...

398
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:38,320
in cultivating new painters
and new artists.

399
00:22:38,519 --> 00:22:39,360
And what did you get?

400
00:22:42,039 --> 00:22:43,840
How many Xun Ran will there be?

401
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:47,519
Moreover, Xun Ran's success
is just because of luck.

402
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:51,080
Think about all the marketing fees
that you had spent on him.

403
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,639
And because you are...

404
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:57,360
too partial to Xun Ran's artworks,

405
00:22:57,560 --> 00:23:00,320
it leads to the losses of
many painters' resources.

406
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,639
Everything that Xun Ran has today...

407
00:23:02,879 --> 00:23:04,320
is what he deserves.

408
00:23:04,519 --> 00:23:06,960
His works are highly recognised
in the market.

409
00:23:07,080 --> 00:23:08,440
I have no need to be partial.

410
00:23:08,639 --> 00:23:10,560
What about this gallery?

411
00:23:13,999 --> 00:23:15,039
This is such a huge place.

412
00:23:15,320 --> 00:23:17,320
It must have costed a lot of money.

413
00:23:17,639 --> 00:23:20,879
Are all of our other galleries going to
bear the costs for this?

414
00:23:21,999 --> 00:23:24,919
And then, some experts
who you've hired...

415
00:23:25,119 --> 00:23:28,039
will put them in the account under
the name of various projects, right?

416
00:23:28,399 --> 00:23:29,919
What will you get from that?

417
00:23:30,399 --> 00:23:33,039
You'll only drag the performance
of the galleries down.

418
00:23:34,039 --> 00:23:36,080
You'll drag down the
entire gallery business.

419
00:23:36,320 --> 00:23:37,639
You've said so much.

420
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:40,239
But it's still because of him, right?

421
00:23:40,999 --> 00:23:42,879
You want to force Xun Ran to leave.

422
00:23:43,119 --> 00:23:44,159
On the contrary,

423
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:47,119
since you already spent
so much money on him,

424
00:23:48,159 --> 00:23:50,840
I'm planning to commercialise him...

425
00:23:51,039 --> 00:23:52,960
and maximize his business value.

426
00:23:53,119 --> 00:23:56,279
Only by doing so can I increase
the turnover of Yun Ma Artwork.

427
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:58,080
And the galleries' economy
won't be dragged down.

428
00:23:58,239 --> 00:23:58,919
You can't do that.

429
00:24:00,119 --> 00:24:03,039
Xun Ran, his father and my husband...

430
00:24:03,239 --> 00:24:04,639
are real artists.

431
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:06,960
They should just focus
on their creations.

432
00:24:07,159 --> 00:24:09,519
And you are just wallowing
in degeneration.

433
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:12,039
I don't care if money is
the only thing in your mind.

434
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:14,960
But I'll never allow you
to corrupt him with your...

435
00:24:15,159 --> 00:24:17,200
-money-oriented mind.
-Artist?

436
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:20,239
You know it too.

437
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:23,440
His father, that artist,
passed away because of starvation.

438
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:25,239
And he ended up in the orphanage.

439
00:24:25,759 --> 00:24:28,080
If it wasn't because
you and father took him in,

440
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:30,440
-he might be begging on the street now!
-Shut your mouth.

441
00:24:30,919 --> 00:24:32,159
Don't forget this.

442
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:36,200
Yun Ma is so successful right now
because I'm money-oriented.

443
00:24:36,320 --> 00:24:38,320
That's why you can play with
your art here without worries.

444
00:24:39,159 --> 00:24:41,159
Leave. Leave now!

445
00:24:41,674 --> 00:24:44,200
Leave. Leave now!

446
00:24:45,279 --> 00:24:46,919
Zhou Shi!

447
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,279
Zhou Shi.

448
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:51,159
Director He.

449
00:24:51,519 --> 00:24:52,919
Send the chairman out.

450
00:24:53,399 --> 00:24:56,320
From now on, don't allow him
to step into the gallery at all.

451
00:24:58,320 --> 00:24:59,080
Understood.

452
00:25:00,560 --> 00:25:01,279
Wei...

453
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,399
Chairman.

454
00:25:03,999 --> 00:25:04,840
Alright.

455
00:25:05,919 --> 00:25:06,919
I understand now.

456
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:13,159
You would rather be against
the entire board...

457
00:25:13,360 --> 00:25:15,279
to protect your own selfishness.

458
00:25:16,320 --> 00:25:18,200
I'll deal with this accordingly.

459
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,239
See you in the board meeting.

460
00:25:21,039 --> 00:25:21,919
One more thing.

461
00:25:23,639 --> 00:25:25,560
I won't come to this place ever again.

462
00:25:26,119 --> 00:25:28,480
No. Should I say,

463
00:25:29,279 --> 00:25:30,639
it won't exist anymore.

464
00:25:32,999 --> 00:25:34,119
What are you going to do?

465
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:39,279
You know best about
what I can do, right?

466
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:43,239
Wei Qing, let me warn you.

467
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:46,039
You only have 30% of the gallery shares.

468
00:25:46,320 --> 00:25:47,999
Don't think that you can
act as you please.

469
00:25:48,279 --> 00:25:49,480
It has been so many years.

470
00:25:50,639 --> 00:25:52,480
This is the first time
you called my name.

471
00:25:54,039 --> 00:25:57,119
I never thought that
it'll be under this situation.

472
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:58,519
I know.

473
00:25:58,919 --> 00:26:01,480
You've been wanting to get rid
of this burden, the gallery.

474
00:26:01,879 --> 00:26:04,039
But it is my husband's legacy.

475
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:06,840
I won't allow you to destroy it!

476
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,480
Don't forget.

477
00:26:17,039 --> 00:26:20,279
Your husband is my father too.

478
00:26:21,919 --> 00:26:23,560
The things that you told me...

479
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:26,080
are the things that
I want to tell you too.

480
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:30,480
I hope that you won't
destroy the gallery.

481
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,200
Don't care about him.

482
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:58,800
Let him be.

483
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:00,720
Zhou Shi.

484
00:27:00,919 --> 00:27:02,560
Are you pitying him?

485
00:27:02,759 --> 00:27:03,879
He treated you like that.

486
00:27:03,999 --> 00:27:05,879
Don't be so kind-hearted.

487
00:27:06,119 --> 00:27:08,680
Those are just crocodile tears.
Don't be fooled by him.

488
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:31,360
Cancel the board meeting this afternoon.

489
00:27:31,600 --> 00:27:34,239
-We'll discuss about the time again.
-Alright.

490
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:37,039
By the way. About Xue Zi,

491
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,879
when is she coming back again?

492
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:42,680
She came back yesterday. And...

493
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:44,759
-And?
-She came to this gallery...

494
00:27:44,919 --> 00:27:47,360
and purchase one of Xun Ran's
painting with a high price.

495
00:27:51,360 --> 00:27:53,759
Go back first. I want to be alone.

496
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,680
Do you want me to leave the car here?

497
00:27:55,879 --> 00:27:58,840
-You have to meet Miss Xue later.
-No need.

498
00:27:59,399 --> 00:28:01,759
I'll call you if I need a car.

499
00:28:11,999 --> 00:28:13,200
This is not right!

500
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:16,320
I told you so many times already!
Why can't you change?

501
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:18,680
No matter what I draw,
you'll think that it's wrong.

502
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:19,919
You are bias against me.

503
00:28:20,080 --> 00:28:22,119
I can never draw as good as
the child you picked up.

504
00:28:23,919 --> 00:28:25,119
What nonsense is that?

505
00:28:27,279 --> 00:28:29,279
Since you like the one you
picked up so much,

506
00:28:29,399 --> 00:28:30,759
why did you give birth to me back then?

507
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,999
You have never trust me.

508
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:37,720
You only care about that bastard!

509
00:28:43,159 --> 00:28:44,800
How old are you?
How could you drink every day?

510
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:47,600
-When are you going to practice drawing?
-None of your business.

511
00:28:47,759 --> 00:28:49,360
You have no rights to discipline me.

512
00:28:49,519 --> 00:28:50,919
You are too immature!

513
00:28:54,039 --> 00:28:56,639
It's your fault that
your father is dead!

514
00:28:56,639 --> 00:28:58,480
-Stand up!
-Yun Ma Artwork that was...

515
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:00,239
established by me and my wife...

516
00:29:00,399 --> 00:29:02,680
will be took over by my son,
Wei Qing, after my passing.

517
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:04,119
He'll have full authority.

518
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:06,759
Impossible.

519
00:29:07,519 --> 00:29:08,720
Yun Ma belongs to us.

520
00:29:08,919 --> 00:29:10,279
How could you give it to him?

521
00:29:11,080 --> 00:29:14,680
-Lawyer, have you gotten it wrongly?
-Mother!

